Artwork by [Isabella Lee  
](http://isabellaleephotography.webs.com/)  
**[Audience](http://www.facebook.com/pages/Audience/132660253421759)** are a two piece, made up of Justin and Rémi, two friends that have only just begun to make music together. The result is an atmospheric and minimal sound; the various elements are barely held together, each sound cobbled together in a delightfully improvised way. At times it feels like electronic jazz, with a heart half seduced by modern ambient beat music. Stream and download the new single below.
